metadata.name: A Prototype KryptoKatana
metadata.description:
This Katana is one of the first crafted within the blacksmith's forge, but the many attempts of the ancient druid to imbue it with power left it faded and brittle.
It is no longer fit for combat but is now a keepsake to hold onto.

The clans may yet find use for it.
metadata.creator: Bit Citizen
